dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: Great! The engineer's ball is black tie this year.

dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: I will be renting a tuxedo for the ball, and I would like it if you could keep any snide comments to yourself.

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: Gosh, even I wouldn't make fun of a guy who would pay sixty-five bucks to wear borrowed pants.
